OL,3,CGifted Ghana toddler sets world record
OL,4,Cas youngest male artist
OL,6,FA boy in Ghana has set the record as
OL,7,Fthe world's youngest male artist after
OL,8,Fexhibiting and selling his own
OL,9,Fpaintings at the age of one.
OL,11,FAce-Liam Ankrah held his first
OL,12,Fexhibition at the Museum of Science
OL,13,Fand Technology in Accra in January,
OL,14,Fbut was awarded the title by the
OL,15,FGuinness Book of World Records last
OL,16,Fweek.
OL,18,FOut of 10 pieces he exhibited, nine
OL,19,Fwere sold.
