OL,7,Fwho helped organise the exhibition -
OL,8,Fdid not say how much they sold for.
OL,10,FLast week, the confirmed Ace-Liam as
OL,11,Fthe record holder for the youngest
OL,12,Fmale artist.
OL,14,FMs Eghan, who is also an artist, said
OL,15,Fher son developed his passion for
OL,16,Fafter discovering her acrylic paints
OL,17,Fat just six months old.
