OL,3,CGifted Ghana toddler sets world record
OL,4,Cas youngest male artist
OL,6,FMs Eghan told the Guiness World
OL,7,FRecords: "While learning to crawl, I
OL,8,Fspread out a piece of unstretched
OL,9,Fcanvas on the floor and dropped some
OL,10,Fpaint on it as a way to keep him busy
OL,11,Fwhile I worked on a commission
OL,12,Fpainting.
OL,14,F"He ended up spreading the paint all
OL,15,Fover the canvas, and in the process he
OL,16,Fcreated his first masterpiece titled
OL,17,FThe Crawl.
OL,19,F"It was clear that he found a lot of
OL,20,Fjoy in it."
