OL,3,CGifted Ghana toddler sets world record
OL,4,Cas youngest male artist
OL,6,FThe young artist's talent has
OL,7,Fattracted national and international
OL,8,Fmedia attention, as well as the First
OL,9,FLady of the Republic of .
OL,11,FSince Ace-Liam started talking, he
OL,12,Fwould ask to paint, his mother said.
OL,14,F"His abstract paintings are inspired
OL,15,Fby the world around him; colours,
OL,16,Fshapes, textures and his mood," Ms
OL,17,FEghan told the Guiness World Records.
OL,19,F"Every painting is an expression of
OL,20,Fhis curiosity and joy in discovering
OL,21,Fnew things," she said.
