OL,3,CGifted Ghana toddler sets world record
OL,4,Cas youngest male artist
OL,6,FAce-Liam's family hope to secure
OL,7,Finternational scholarships to nurture
OL,8,Fhis skills, as well as opportunities
OL,9,Ffor him to sell his masterpieces.
OL,11,FHis mother said she hopes the media
OL,12,Fattention around her son could inspire
OL,13,Fother parents to discover and nurture
OL,14,Ftheir children's talents.
OL,16,F"Every child is unique, and nurturing
OL,17,Ftheir passions can lead to amazing
OL,18,Fdiscoveries and achievements," Ms
OL,19,FEghan told the Guiness World Records.
